### HiP-HoP simulations of Pax6 : full set of conformations ###############

A set of 200 simulated conformations is given for each of the three cell 
types Pax6-OFF, Pax6-ON and Pax6-HIGH as detailed in the paper.

Conformations are given in the LAMMPS dump file format 
(see https://lammps.sandia.gov/), which can, for example, be imported 
directly by the molecular graphics software VMD 
(https://www.ks.uiuc.edu/Research/vmd/).

Atom IDs 1-5000 are chromatin beads. Other atoms are TFs.

